    "Due to the numerous test available for diagnosis, their data type also varies.",
    "In a few works, this is leveraged to construct DL models that fit for particular data types.",
    "In Basaia et al. (2019) constructed and verified a DL algorithm for prediction of diagnosis for MCI and AD.",
